{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e240a1f761","title":"视察徐水时的谈话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b5e36caa0b","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"e240a1f761","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1cfda8b396","type":"title","text":"视察徐水时的谈话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"416b41de6e","type":"paragraph","text":"其实粮食多了还是好！多了，国家不要，农业社员自己多吃麻！一天吃五顿也行嘛！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74cbba3a68","type":"paragraph","text":"这妇女解放得很彻底理！是呀！人人都吃食堂，社社都办幼儿园…","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee25555c16","type":"paragraph","text":"这个县是十一万多劳力，抽出了四万多搞水利、打机井、办工业，只有七万多人搞农业嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4834a2a1d2","type":"paragraph","text":"他们这又解放妇女劳力，又搞军事化，全县农业搞了九十多个团，两百多个营，他们就是这个办法喱！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2aae993b04","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这粮食吃不完，怎么办呀！粮食多了，以后就少种一些，一天做半天活儿，另外半天搞文化，学科学，闹文化娱乐，办大学、中学，你们看好么？祝你们丰收！秋收我要有时间的话，再来看你们。这里的干劲不小喱！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a49a9bf448","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上的事情是不办就不办，一办就办得很多！过去几千年都是亩产一二百斤，你看，如今一下子就是几于上万！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fe5c4073f","type":"paragraph","text":"要早抓明年的粮食规划，要多种小麦，多种油料作物，种菜也要多品种，这样来满足人民的需要","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ded6e2c8c1","type":"paragraph","text":"小麦地一定要深翻，翻到一尺以上。以后人民就主要吃小麦，玉米和山药喂鞋口，喂猪；猪喂多了，人民就多吃肉。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"58027c65bc","type":"paragraph","text":"下边真好啊！出的东西真多啊！北京就不出什么东西。你们说，北京出什么啊","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":517,"end":516}},"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"54fa75d1d3","type":"paragraph","text":"要早抓明年的粮食规划，要多种小麦，多种油料作物，种菜也要多品种，这样来满足人民的需要。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57c0413c90","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上的事情是不办就不办，一办就办得很多！过去几千年都是亩产一二百斤，你看，如今一下子就是几千上万！","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"712b46ed3c","type":"title","text":"视察徐水时的谈话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"950ad64f81","type":"paragraph","text":"这个县是十一万多劳力，抽出了四万多搞水利、打机井、办工业，只有七万多人搞农业嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7e53f14a3","type":"paragraph","text":"他们这又解放妇女劳力，又搞军事化，全县农业搞了九十多个团，两百多个营，他们就是这个办法哩！","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7caa11b1a","type":"paragraph","text":"小麦地一定要深翻，翻到一尺以上。以后人民就主要吃小麦，玉米和山药喂牲口，喂猪；猪喂多了，人民就多吃肉。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e109770e2e","type":"paragraph","text":"下边真好啊！出的东西真多啊！北京就不出什么东西。你们说，北京出什么啊？（徐水县委书记说：北京出政治领导，出党的总路线！）","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4208e5406","type":"paragraph","text":"这妇女解放得很彻底哩！是呀！人人都吃食堂，社社都办幼儿园。......","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1ede70de9","type":"paragraph","text":"其实粮食多了还是好！多了，国家不要，农业社员自己多吃嘛！一天吃五顿也行嘛！","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd1ba4b166","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这粮食吃不完，怎么办呀！粮食多了，以后就少种一些，一天做半天活儿，另外半天搞文化、学科学、闹文化娱乐、办大学、中学，你们看好么？祝你们丰收！秋收我要有时间的话，再来看你们。这里的干劲不小哩！","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"e240a1f761","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":198,"end":197}}}},"__N_SSG":true}